      "span_text": "Biological hypotheses have provided a priori evidence of mechanistic relevance [CITATION_2] , but existing targeted hypothesis-driven approaches are likely to miss out numerous genes related to the biological hypotheses, requiring new alternative approaches to find many hypothesis-relevant genes."
